name: Quadrahead Media
overview:
Quadrahead was founded in 1997, quickly gained popularity with consumers and brands, achieving success through online acquisition, retention and branding.

Largely behind the scenes, the company provides advertising services to businesses and creates solutions that take advantage of the consumer sales cycle and ecosystem. Various programs designed for mobile, display, search advertising, social mediums, Quadrahead focuses on conceptualizing and executing programs as well. They are an end-to-end performance focused organization helping brands navigate through the ever evolving consumer ecosystem to make better advertising decisions.
